END, [x].[CategoryId] AS [Id0], [x.BlogCategory].[Name] AS [Name0], [x.BlogCategory].[Description] AS [Description0], [x.BlogCategory].[ParentId], [x.BlogCategory].[HomeOrder], [x.BlogCategory].[Image] AS [Image0], [x.BlogCategory].[HomeFlag] AS [HomeFlag0], [x.BlogCategory].[DateCreated], [x.BlogCategory].[DateModified], [x.BlogCategory].[SortOrder], [x.BlogCategory].[Status], [x.BlogCategory].[SeoPageTitle], [x.BlogCategory].[SeoAlias], [x.BlogCategory].[SeoKeywords], [x.BlogCategory].[SeoDescription], [x].[DateCreated] AS [DateCreated0], [x].[DateModified] AS [DateModified0], [x].[Status] AS [Status0], [x].[SeoPageTitle] AS [SeoPageTitle0], [x].[SeoAlias] AS [SeoAlias0], [x].[SeoKeywords] AS [SeoKeywords0], [x].[SeoDescription] AS [SeoDescription0], [x.BlogCategory].[Id]
FROM [Blogs] AS [x]
LEFT JOIN [BlogCategories] AS [x.BlogCategory] ON [x].[CategoryId] = [x.BlogCategory].[Id]
WHERE [x].[Status] = 1
